text: Journal Press was a weekly newspaper based in King George, Virginia covering King George and Wesmoreland Counties and the Town of Colonial Beach, Virginia. The newspaper's final edition was January 11, 2017.Dyson, Cathy, "Journal paper closing next month, barring 'a miracle'", December 23, 2016. ==References== Category:Defunct newspapers published in Virginia Category:King George County, Virginia Category:Westmoreland County, Virginia
title: Journal Press
